'''Oridium''' was an ore found on [[Vulcar]],<ref name="The Essential Atlas">''[[The Essential Atlas]]''</ref> [[Gavos]]<ref name="Debts to Pay">{{FFG|story=Debts to Pay|book=Star Wars: Edge of the Empire Game Master's Kit|text=''Star Wars'': Edge of the Empire Game Master's Kit}}</ref> and in the [[Arah asteroid belt|Belt of Arah]]. The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] operated an [[Arah mining facility|Oridium ore processing plant]] in the Belt and the oridium was eventually used in the production of [[TIE/ph "Phantom" Multi-Role Stealth Starfighter/Legends|TIE Phantoms]].

